OL,5,G0015 Nina Simone: The Lost Album
OL,6,     FSpotlighting a lost album from one
OL,7,     Fof the most gifted vocalists of
OL,8,     Fher generation, unearth new
OL,9,     Fstories relating to the iconic
OL,10,     Fsinger-songwriter Nina Simone.
OL,11,     FDiscriminatory language.
OL,12,G0145 Nina Simone: Live At Montreux 1976
